MooseX-AbstractFactory version 0.0.1

Implements a Class::Factory-style AbstractFactory as a Moose role. 


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

Alternatively, to install with Module::Build, you can use the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install


DEPENDENCIES

Moose


